{"type": "article", "id": 49864, "title": "康泰纳仕推出摄影行为守则，以及，优衣库发布联名睡衣系列 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-02T04:02:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 2182, "name": "康泰纳仕"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}, {"id": 47537, "name": "Ralph Laurent"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180202115015N4hQcxfqFMOSdmnK.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Conde-Nast-introduces-code-of-conduct-for-photo-shoots,942990.html#.WnO7hJP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>应对性骚扰，Vogue 母公司、康泰纳仕集团发布杂志摄影行为守则</strong></a> | 守则包括，所有模特儿必须年满 18 岁，否则需要指派专人陪同。保证模特换衣服的绝对私密；禁止一对一相处，无论是摄影师、化妆师还是工作人员等。为了制定守则，康泰纳仕邀请了 150 位业内人士，成立了一个高级管理委员会。 </p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Guess-shares-slump-after-model-Kate-Upton-tweets-about-executive,943265.html#.WnPNWZP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Guess 创意总监被指控性骚扰，集团股价大跌</strong></a> | Guess 联合创始人、现任创意总监兼董事会副主席 Paul Marciano 被指控性骚扰。超模 Kate Upton 在 Instagram 上指出，在与 Paul Marciano 出席活动时遭到性骚扰，Guess 仍让他担任重要职务，实在令人失望。消息传出后，周四，Guess 集团的股价下跌了 14.1%，市值蒸发约 2 亿美元。 </p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Ralph-Lauren-s-turnaround-efforts-yet-to-pay-off,943241.html#.WnPalJP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Ralph Lauren 业绩不佳，季度亏损 8180 万美元</strong></a> | Ralph Lauren 的最新财报显示，截止至去年 12 月 30 日的三个月内，净收入下降了 4.4%，亏损 8180 万美元。其中，中国大陆地区收入增长了 28%，北美地区销售额下降11%，至 8.84 亿美元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>3 月 2 日至 28 日，在东京自由之丘 IDEE SHOP 三楼的画廊，将举办一场名为 <a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-02/ideeshop-artposter/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lyrical Abstraction: Vintage/Rare Art Poster Exhibition </a>的艺术海报展，感兴趣的话不妨去看看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802021148289HlZpqaMWfmj4xAk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>意大利奢侈皮具品牌<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-01/valextra-kumakengo/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Valextra</a>，请来隈研吾设计了它在米兰的精品店。 </p><p>店铺设计以“森林”为主题，整个空间里重复出现 136 块树干切面，包包摆放在“树”上，营造出了森林的效果。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114807d0xVKlQo7PcYkzSt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.616667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802021148144xCtiN8kvJES31eu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.677273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114808x3NG5PCJjYIOhd6a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114807qIxFQ4Tin7Nlgryf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334848\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114808NhFYecJpMbgRPUuO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114814UTyEq1htWGsSXuDl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>今年是 Y-3 系列诞生的 15 周年。在<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/y-3-ss18-campaign-chapter-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Y-3 的 2018 春夏系列</a>里，山本耀司和 adidas 在沿用了品牌标志性的简约设计之上，为其注入了新的活力，比如找来山本耀司的老搭档 Taishi Hayashi 创作的眼镜蛇图案，Alessio Bolzoni 拍的 lookbook 也还不错。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114722sJNBLRmu2EwfqgyO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114722qhrUTce9I7mGEaoL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114722ZU0PINQVeXx9qtEg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114723sxriQARYVaeygK0b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114724mxaXortTup4zGbVg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114724c4nytT7Cr0Vj9Yox.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114724IzLZ7Apx3ruXwOcT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114734PQO381YVXJwETgkb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114736cpvZiwy81EbzxFnV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114737YvKWmsREeMS7iCBh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114737lkOxWq63S5fpK2V4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114737DlNXPCfwUS7hZpmJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114739Af2rkTvY17IzmHXC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114745pw5PWSKd1ikL4tAn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802021147460yvFkzMoLSJXnZ8Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114747ZvStb83QsTgowphJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114747t31U6qi7TlsomMeJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802021147487gxIGMAYyVZ958nh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802021147488DR54MabeEsvJQL9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114748FHk7uMAQTJfPEq5j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114749hoksiABFwDGvrPaS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114748GjQSDJCFNthuWOiA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114753CUEY18loRviGp2Om.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Vans 的新 campaign：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vanscustomculture/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans Custom Culture Competition </a>开始，Vans 号召全美的高中生加入，设计自己的 slip on，最后选出的优胜者将获得高达 7.5 万美元的奖励。 </p><p>来看看现在都有哪些惊悚的设计：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114652t3B9iXuwpcCdaDfk.png\" data-ratio=\"1.088415\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114650BnNfw2qXDWYPU5Sp.png\" data-ratio=\"0.989933\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114652KTBzbW605adrQNgX.png\" data-ratio=\"1.240084\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802021146546TfmpUkWcb9gR0AG.png\" data-ratio=\"0.980000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114656lZmhsjDL10OXKSHM.png\" data-ratio=\"0.998328\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/549205\" rel=\"nofollow\">H&amp;M 为平昌冬奥会设计了瑞典代表团的制服</a>，这也是继里约奥运会之后，H&amp;M 再度为国家队做设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114503gDQeXvCtpAnJPUcz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.732000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114504W8wYbfSTDx2HJMkj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114503ilRdf5YIpHxgrmnD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.724000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114513UZpQ7MkXgGljJBKY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.525000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114523dUJ73OIZr1mfwc05.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.652500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/549191\" rel=\"nofollow\">优衣库和法国模特 Ines de la Fressange 的同名品牌合作</a>，将推出首个联名睡衣系列。此外，双方的联名款还包括 T 恤、连衣裙、外套等 82 款单品，价格范围在 1990 至 12900 日元之间，将于 2 月 23 日开始在日本全国开售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114431Ukp4emLIK86fcVn1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114434YO0shfleugQWErIG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114354bvPjt4rD6cpqaSN3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667780\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114433eA6wuWLNjnmSgPXp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114351gWyMjY145sn8I6Eu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.476380\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202114227wZuFiKRQDPsrVA9C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018020211422